  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个查询处理流程的类图。核心是一个Query类，它要有validate和rules两个方法，用来校验查询条件。然后需要QueryHandler来实际处理这个Query。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Query",
        "validate",
        "rules",
        "QueryHandler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Query负责校验，QueryHandler负责执行。那QueryHandler的handle方法需要接收Query作为参数吗？还是通过其他方式关联？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QueryHandler",
        "handle",
        "Query"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，handle方法要明确接收Query对象作为入参。另外，数据从哪来？我们需要ReadModel，它封装了数据访问，有find和findAll方法，还有id和attributes属性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QueryHandler",
        "handle",
        "Query",
        "ReadModel",
        "find",
        "findAll",
        "id",
        "attributes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Query、QueryHandler和ReadModel画出来，方法属性都标上。现在QueryHandler和ReadModel之间是什么关系？直接调用吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Query",
        "QueryHandler",
        "ReadModel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "QueryHandler要从ReadModel里检索数据，所以是\"retrieves from\"的关系。但这里有个问题——查询结果不能直接返回原始数据，得包装一下。我们加个QueryResult类，有data和meta两个属性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QueryHandler",
        "ReadModel",
        "QueryResult",
        "data",
        "meta"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "QueryResult作为返回载体，data存结果，meta存分页之类的元信息。那ReadModel到QueryResult的关系是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QueryResult",
        "data",
        "meta",
        "ReadModel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ReadModel把原始数据\"transformed to\" QueryResult。另外Query和QueryHandler之间，Query是被QueryHandler处理的，标成\"processed by\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ReadModel",
        "QueryResult",
        "Query",
        "QueryHandler",
        "processed by",
        "transformed to"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个流程是：Query被校验后交给QueryHandler处理，Handler从ReadModel检索数据，再转换成QueryResult返回。三个关系都标注清楚了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Query",
        "QueryHandler",
        "ReadModel",
        "QueryResult",
        "processed by",
        "retrieves from",
        "transformed to"
      ],
